

URL = http://www.openmetaverse.org/


=Description=

"The Open Metaverse Foundation is a non-profit organization founded with the mandate of developing open technologies and open-source software related to the metaverse and virtual worlds. The OMF provides support and guidance to selected projects that espouse the principles of the foundation."


=Principles=

"Principles of the Open Metaverse Foundation

* The software and technologies of the metaverse should be open and freely available for everyone to use and modify without encumbrance by patents.
    
* The software and technologies of the metaverse should avoid imposing restriction on user autonomy.
    
* The software and technologies of the metaverse should protect user privacy.
    
* The software and technologies of the metaverse should require only information necessary for its operation.
    
* The software and technologies of the metaverse should not discriminate against any person, group of persons, or fields of endeavor."
(http://www.openmetaverse.org/about)


